summary:
- **General Meeting Results**: All resolutions passed by poll.  
- **Key Resolutions**:  
  - Approval for issuance of Convertible Notes (Tranche 1 and Tranche 2) – carried (~88% support).  
  - Approval for free attaching and broker options – carried (~88% and ~88% support, respectively).  
  - Approval for Performance Rights to directors (Greenaway, Gale, Vilensky, Wiener) – carried (78.5%–86.7% support).  
  - Approval for share issuance to acquire Cummins Project – carried (~99.7% support).  

**No other material trading or capital markets information identified.**
